notes

- run the command below to install the expo fonts package dependency:
expo install expo-font

- nice to read: library to check the react native elements
https://github.com/GeekyAnts/NativeBase
https://github.com/react-native-training/react-native-elements

- use 'flex: 1' style to scroll view components works properly in android.

- use the key-value below to configure the app's orientation.
App.json: {
    "orientation": "default",
    "orientation": "portrait",
    "orientation": "landscape",
}

- always use KeyboardAvoidingView inside of ScrollView

- install 'expo install expo-screen-orientation' to lock orientation async landscape/portrait by user
use import { ScreenOrientation } from 'expo'; or import * as ScreenOrientation from 'expo-screen-orientation;
